      "source_content": "---\nslug: atomic-css-in-js\ntitle: Atomic CSS-in-JS\ndescription: Atomic CSS-in-JS... or how to scale your CSS-in-JS.\nauthors: [slorber]\ntwitterThreadUrl: \"https://slo.im/thread\"\nimage: ./images/hero.png\n---",
